As light turns into darkness, we run through the night Stopping for breath, as we hold each other tight Nothing can pull us apart, we'll always be together You know I'll always love you,  forever and ever As the sun shines down, love shine in your eyes And your smile is like
stars twinkling in the sky My heart races from your touch on my skin
I can't believe I found you, Love's first win.

Elisabrth was born and raised in Eau Claire, WI. After high school, she moved to Menomonie to attend the University of Wisconsin-Stout, where her passion for history was born. After two years in Menomonie, Elisabeth moved back to Eau Claire to attend University of Wisconsin-Eau Claire where she graduated
with a degree in history.Elisabeth's past times include shopping, shopping, and more shopping (with coupons, of course)!

Vincent was born and raised in Marshfield, WI. Throughout elementary school, junior high, and high school, he was always outside playing football, playing basketball, skateboarding, and snowboarding. During the cold and rainy days, Vincent and his friends would play video games into the wee hours of the morning. After graduating high school, Vincent moved to Menomonie, WI to attend the University of Wisconsin-Stout. During this time, he developed a knack for web design and web development.

We’ve met one summer night in the club. The music was to loud so we really didn’t speak that much. One great thing led to another and the rest is history.

All guests are required to ride a shuttle to the ceremony. The shuttle will depart Cannon River Winery at 3:45pm. Please arrive promptly as not to delay the start of the celebration. Reception immediately to follow at Cannon River Winery’s Event Center.

We have reserved 25 rooms at Treasure Island Resort (under Ashley Jensen) with free shuttle service to and from the reception. The hotel is about a 15-20 minute drive from Cannon Falls. Shuttles depart from the hotel at 3:30pm

Our wedding will be held at the Cannon River Winery in Cannon Falls, Minnesota. The ceremony will take place outdoors at Cannon River Winery’s vineyard nestled in the beautiful Sogn Valley followed by the reception at the winery.
